{{Spritebox/Header|type=Ghost|type2=Ground}}\n{{Spritebox/NA|gen=VII}}\n{{Spritebox/7|ndex=769}}\n{{Spritebox/Footer|769|Sandygast}}\n\n==Trivia==\n* Sandygast has the lowest base {{stat|Speed}} stat of all {{type|Ghost}} Pokémon.\n\n===Origin===\nSandygast resembles a basic {{wp|Sand art and play|sand castle}} with a tunnel and shovel. Its {{Shiny}} color variation may be based on {{wp|black sand}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nSandygast may be a combination of \'\'sandy\'\' and \'\'ghast\'\' (evil spirit).\n\nSunaba may derive from 砂場 \'\'sunaba\'\' (sandbox) or 砂 \'\'suna\'\' (sand) and \'\'bar\'\' or いないいないばあ \'\'inai-inai-baa\'\' ({{wp|peekaboo}}).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Ghost|type2=Ground\n|ja=スナバァ \'\'Sunaba\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|砂場 \'\'sunaba\'\'|sandbox}} or {{tt|砂 \'\'suna\'\'|sand}}, \'\'bar\'\', and {{tt|いないいないばあ \'\'inai-inai-baa\'\'|peekaboo}}\n|fr=Bacabouh|frmeaning=From {{tt|\'\'bac à sable\'\'|sandbox}} and {{tt|\'\'bouh\'\'|boo}}\n|es=Sandygast|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Sankabuh|demeaning=From {{tt|\'\'Sandkasten\'\'|sandbox}} and {{tt|\'\'buh\'\'|boo}}\n|it=Sandygast|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=모래꿍 \'\'Moraekkung\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|모래 \'\'morae\'\'|sand}}, {{tt|까꿍 \'\'kkakkung\'\'|peekaboo}}, and {{tt|궁 (宮) \'\'gung\'\'|palace}}.\n|zh_cmn=沙丘娃 \'\'Shāqiūwá\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|沙丘 \'\'shāqiū\'\'|sand dune}}, {{tt|娃 \'\'wá\'\'|child}}, and {{tt|哇 \'\'wa\'\'|interjection indicating surprise or shock}}\n|zh_yue=沙丘娃 \'\'Sāyāuwā\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|沙丘 \'\'sāyāu\'\'|sand dune}}, {{tt|娃 \'\'wā\'\'|child}}, and {{tt|哇 \'\'wā\'\'|interjection indicating surprise or shock}}\n|ru=Сэндигаст \'\'Sendigast\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name}}\n{{-}}\n\n==Notes==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Ghost|type2=Ground}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Ghost|prevnum=768|prev=Golisopod|nextnum=770|next=Palossand}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Sankabuh]]\n[[